03:29.233 --> 03:34.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It took him several years
to sober up and restart
his life and career.

03:36.233 --> 03:40.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JASON ISBELL: Before I stopped
drinking, I thought, if I quit
drinking, am I still going

03:40.500 --> 03:41.733 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
