03:41.733 --> 03:42.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Am I still going to
be a good songwriter?

03:42.966 --> 03:44.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Am I going to still be
a rock 'n' roll person?

03:44.433 --> 03:47.133 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Are people going to still
want to be around me?

03:47.133 --> 03:50.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
