04:02.233 --> 04:06.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: But I can
see where the anxiety
comes from, because, I
mean, in your business,

04:06.200 --> 04:10.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
