between kind of making it and
not making it or having success

04:10.933 --> 04:11.933 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
or not?

04:11.933 --> 04:12.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JASON ISBELL: Yes.

04:12.933 --> 04:14.866 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Yes, it's hard.

04:14.866 --> 04:17.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's really hard to make a
living writing songs and singing
them, really, really hard.

04:17.966 --> 04:22.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
A lot of people, they try it
out like as a lottery ticket.

04:22.066 --> 04:24.933 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And then, if it doesn't work,
they go do something else.

04:24.933 --> 04:27.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But that's not the
tradition that I come from.

04:27.000 --> 04:32.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I come from a group of people
who pretty much set themselves
to do this for the rest of

04:33.166 --> 04:34.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
