it kills them or not.

04:34.666 --> 04:36.366 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And that's how I was early on.

04:36.366 --> 04:38.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That's how I still am.

04:38.500 --> 04:43.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
